                            <comment id="15195700" author="jira-bot" created="Tue, 15 Mar 2016 17:19:25 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Commit 1735145 from &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/ViewProfile.jspa?name=tilman&quot; class=&quot;user-hover&quot; rel=&quot;tilman&quot;&gt;tilman&lt;/a&gt; in branch &apos;pdfbox/trunk&apos;&lt;br/&gt;
[ &lt;a href=&quot;https://svn.apache.org/r1735145&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://svn.apache.org/r1735145&lt;/a&gt; ]&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/PDFBOX-3273&quot; title=&quot;Fonts not rendered correctly&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;PDFBOX-3273&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;PDFBOX-3273&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt;: round result of int division&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="15195737" author="jira-bot" created="Tue, 15 Mar 2016 17:32:56 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Commit 1735148 from &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/ViewProfile.jspa?name=tilman&quot; class=&quot;user-hover&quot; rel=&quot;tilman&quot;&gt;tilman&lt;/a&gt; in branch &apos;pdfbox/branches/2.0&apos;&lt;br/&gt;
[ &lt;a href=&quot;https://svn.apache.org/r1735148&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://svn.apache.org/r1735148&lt;/a&gt; ]&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/PDFBOX-3273&quot; title=&quot;Fonts not rendered correctly&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;PDFBOX-3273&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;PDFBOX-3273&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt;: round result of int division&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="15195740" author="tilman" created="Tue, 15 Mar 2016 17:33:58 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;This mitigates the effect somewhat, &quot;b&quot;, &quot;h&quot; and &quot;s&quot; have some slight flaws. Is this important for you, or is this just some PDF that you tried to see if the software works?&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;A better solution would be to change the classes to use a List&amp;lt;Number&amp;gt;, but each time I&apos;ve started this, it resulted in an incredible mass of follow-up changes that frustrated me so much that I started to press CTRL-Z about a hundred times.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="15197184" author="jacopo.pugliese" created="Wed, 16 Mar 2016 11:04:21 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Thank you for your fix.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;This pdf is important for us, we are not using it for testing (I specified for testing because I was tasked to investigate the problem at hand). However, this pdf is the only one that is causing problems with our workflow so far (we already processed lots of pdf documents with your library), so if we don&apos;t find a solution we won&apos;t simply publish it.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="15198468" author="jahewson" created="Thu, 17 Mar 2016 00:17:04 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Yep, this has been a weakness since the 1.8 days, and as you can see from my TODO comment, I&apos;ve completely dodged having to fix it.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="15198472" author="jahewson" created="Thu, 17 Mar 2016 00:22:26 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Thinking about it, another approach could be to introduce a constant scaling factor so that we&apos;re basically using an integer fixed point representation. Then once the calculations are complete, we scale the path by the factor.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="15223426" author="lehmi" created="Sun, 3 Apr 2016 17:32:02 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;There isn&apos;t any scaling involved when creating the path&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="15223429" author="jira-bot" created="Sun, 3 Apr 2016 17:41:12 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Commit 1737599 from &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/ViewProfile.jspa?name=lehmi&quot; class=&quot;user-hover&quot; rel=&quot;lehmi&quot;&gt;lehmi&lt;/a&gt; in branch &apos;pdfbox/trunk&apos;&lt;br/&gt;
[ &lt;a href=&quot;https://svn.apache.org/r1737599&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://svn.apache.org/r1737599&lt;/a&gt; ]&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/PDFBOX-3273&quot; title=&quot;Fonts not rendered correctly&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;PDFBOX-3273&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;PDFBOX-3273&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt;: replace List&amp;lt;Integer&amp;gt; with List&amp;lt;Number&amp;gt; to increase accuracy&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="15223431" author="lehmi" created="Sun, 3 Apr 2016 17:45:22 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Fontbox now uses List&amp;lt;Number&amp;gt; as proposed by &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/ViewProfile.jspa?name=tilman&quot; class=&quot;user-hover&quot; rel=&quot;tilman&quot;&gt;tilman&lt;/a&gt;. It looks like the rendering is quite perfect now.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;I&apos;ve changed the method signature of CharStringHandler#handleSequence and CharStringHandler#handleCommand. Both are public but IMHO they are supposed to be part of a private part of Fontbox. &lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;WDYT?&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="15223433" author="jira-bot" created="Sun, 3 Apr 2016 17:53:41 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Commit 1737600 from &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/ViewProfile.jspa?name=lehmi&quot; class=&quot;user-hover&quot; rel=&quot;lehmi&quot;&gt;lehmi&lt;/a&gt; in branch &apos;pdfbox/trunk&apos;&lt;br/&gt;
[ &lt;a href=&quot;https://svn.apache.org/r1737600&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://svn.apache.org/r1737600&lt;/a&gt; ]&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/PDFBOX-3273&quot; title=&quot;Fonts not rendered correctly&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;PDFBOX-3273&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;PDFBOX-3273&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt;: fix ClassCastException&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="15223447" author="tilman" created="Sun, 3 Apr 2016 18:38:39 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;No regressions, and no changes in any files except the one here. And yes, these methods are probably not needed to be too public.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="15223492" author="lehmi" created="Sun, 3 Apr 2016 20:11:39 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;So, saying that, w.r.t. 2.0.x it shouldn&apos;t be a breaking change, should it?&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="15223497" author="tilman" created="Sun, 3 Apr 2016 20:15:55 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;IMHO almost nobody uses that API anyway. Those who do will survive this little change.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="15223499" author="lehmi" created="Sun, 3 Apr 2016 20:17:52 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;I just want to hear another opinion before I&apos;m going to apply that change to 2.0.x as well.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="15223500" author="jira-bot" created="Sun, 3 Apr 2016 20:20:11 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Commit 1737606 from &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/ViewProfile.jspa?name=lehmi&quot; class=&quot;user-hover&quot; rel=&quot;lehmi&quot;&gt;lehmi&lt;/a&gt; in branch &apos;pdfbox/branches/2.0&apos;&lt;br/&gt;
[ &lt;a href=&quot;https://svn.apache.org/r1737606&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://svn.apache.org/r1737606&lt;/a&gt; ]&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/PDFBOX-3273&quot; title=&quot;Fonts not rendered correctly&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;PDFBOX-3273&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;PDFBOX-3273&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt;: replace List&amp;lt;Integer&amp;gt; with List&amp;lt;Number&amp;gt; to increase accuracy&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="15223502" author="lehmi" created="Sun, 3 Apr 2016 20:22:47 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;I guess we are done here.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/ViewProfile.jspa?name=jacopo.pugliese&quot; class=&quot;user-hover&quot; rel=&quot;jacopo.pugliese&quot;&gt;jacopo.pugliese&lt;/a&gt; Thanks for the report!&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
